      <div type="edition" xml:lang="pra-Latn">
	<ab>
	  <lb n="1"/>
	    <gap reason="lost" quantity="unknown" unit="character"/>sa 
	    tulakicasa
	    gahapatisa <persName key="pers:Am-Kubula">kubulasa</persName>
	    putasa <persName key="pers:Am-Budhi">budhino</persName>
	    bhāriyāya <persName key="pers:Am-Tukā">tukāya</persName>
	    saputikāya sabhaginikāya paṭo deyadhaṃma
	</ab>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<ab>(This) slab is the pious gift of
	<persName key="pers:Am-Tukā">Tukā</persName>, the wife of
	<persName key="pers:Am-Budhi">Budhi</persName>, son of the
	householder <persName key="pers:Am-Kubula">Kubula</persName>,
	a Tulakica, with her son and sister.</ab>
      </div>
